PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT RESPECTING BIOLOGY CASEWORK ANALYSIS with the Provinces of British Columbia, Alberta, Saskatchewan, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Nova Scotia, Prince Edward Island and Newfoundland and Labrador, and the Governments of Nunavut, Yukon and the Northwest Territories which provides funding for biology casework analysis, effective April 1, 2008 to March 31, 2009, with the possibility of a one year renewal period for 2009-2010.
